{{#if isShowingHowToPlayModal}}
  {{#modal-dialog close='howToPlayDialog' translucentOverlay=true targetAttachment='none' container-class='centered-scrolling-container card flexBlock flexVertical modalShit modalFadeIn ib-container' overlay-class='centered-scrolling-overlay' wrapper-class='centered-scrolling-wrapper'}}
      <p class="u-colorBlueDark u-textLarger">How To Play</p>
      <p class="u-textLeft">
        As a young Ghanaian, your goal is to build a business that will be both profitable and sustainable. Over the course of 12 months, you will face a series of challenges, each of which will require tough decisions that will impact your business and your personal life. It won’t be easy, but as a driven and passionate entrepreneur, you’re up for the task, and down for the adventure!
      </p>
      <p class="u-textLeft">
        First, choose your character. Each character is has a different background, and will face a unique set of challenges as they seek to build a sustainable business over the course of a single year.
      </p>
      <p class="u-textLeft">
        Each month, you will be presented with a new scenario, and given 2 or 3 courses of action to choose from. The decision you make will impact a set of ‘indicators’, which will be located on the left-side of your screen. These include the following:
      </p>
      <p class="u-textLeft">
        <img class="htp-icon" src="/assets/images/icons/Cash.png"/> How much cash you have on hand. Ghana’s official currency is the Ghana Cedi (₵), which is worth about ⅓ of a Canadian dollar
        <br/>
        <img class="htp-icon" src="/assets/images/icons/Debt.png"/> How much money you owe family, friends and creditors. Monthly payments for this debt will come out of your cash each month.
        <br/>
        <img class="htp-icon" src="/assets/images/icons/DebtPayment.png"/> The amount put towards your debt each month.
        <br/>
        <img class="htp-icon" src="/assets/images/icons/MonthlyProfit.png"/> The amount of profit — revenue minus expenses — that your business is making each month. The monthly profit will be added to your cash at the beginning of each month.
        <br/>
        <img class="htp-icon" src="/assets/images/icons/KojoLamisiAssets.png"/> Non-financial assets, including equipment, stored goods, electronics, etc.
        <br/>
        <img class="htp-icon" src="/assets/images/icons/Resilience.png"/> Your ability to adapt to changing circumstances and to overcome unexpected challenges. 
        <br/>
        <img class="htp-icon" src="/assets/images/icons/EnvironmentAllImpact.png"/> Your impact on the natural environment.
        <br/>
      </p>
      <p class="u-textLeft">
        Make sure to monitor these indicators, and change your decisions accordingly. You can click on each of the indicators at any time during the simulation for more information.  At the end of the game, you will get a report on your progress.  
      </p>
      <p class="u-textLeft">
        You are ready to start the game!  <b>Choose your character, and begin your entrepreneurial journey!</b>
      </p>
